'''Espérance Nyirasafari''' ni umunyamategeko akaba n'umunyapolitiki mu [[Rwanda]], akaba umwe muri ba Visi Perezida ba Sena y'u [[Rwanda]], guhera ku ya 17 Ukwakira 2019<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/politiki/amakuru/article/nyirasafari-esperance-wari-minisitiri-w-umuco-na-siporo-yagizwe-senateri</ref>.  Yashyizweho muri Sena na Perezida w'u [[Rwanda]], ku ya 22 Nzeri 2019<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/who-who-new-senate</ref>. 
[[Dosiye:Espérance Nyirasafari 2013-07-01 (35426418905) (cropped).jpg|thumb|Espérance Nyirasafari]]
Mbere yibyo, yabaye [[Inama y’Abaminisitiri|minisitiri]] muri Minisiteri ya Siporo n’umuco, kuva ku ya 18 Ukwakira 2018,  kugeza ku ya 22 Nzeri 2019<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/85878/minisitiri-nyirasafari-esperance-yakiriye-mu-biro-bye-miss-iradukunda-liliane-ugiye-kwitab-85878.html</ref>.  Mbere yibyo, kuva 5 Ukwakira 2016 kugeza 18 Ukwakira 2018, yari Minisitiri w’uburinganire n’iterambere ry’umuryango<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/nyirasafari-raises-red-flag-over-increasing-teenage-pregnancies</ref>. 

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Espérance yavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] ku babyeyi  babanyarwanda; bombi bishwe muri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Jenoside yo mu Rwanda]] mu 1994, akiri muto<ref>https://cnlg.gov.rw/index.php?id=87&L=2&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=3679&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=3e5ed2fc3b1e62f38ca97aa432a1f3d3</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2009, yabaye umunyamabanga uhoraho muri minisiteri y’ubutabera mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201105130229.html</ref>.  , ku ya 5 Ukwakira 2016, bivugwa ko yari umwe mu bagize [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|Inteko ishinga amategeko y'u Rwanda]] <ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/esperance-nyirasafari</ref>.  Yasimbuye [[Diane Gashumba]] aba minisitiri muri Migeprof, wabaye Minisitiri w’ubuzima mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/politiki/amakuru/article/nyirasafari-esperance-wari-minisitiri-w-umuco-na-siporo-yagizwe-senateri</ref>.  Mu ivugurura ry’abaminisitiri ryo ku ya 31 Kanama 2017, Espérance Nyirasafari yagumanye inshingano ze muri Migeprof<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/214047</ref>.  Nka minisitiri  ashyigikiye kubahana hagati y’abashakanye kugira ngo bateze imbere umuryango<ref>https://rwanda.unfpa.org/en/news/gender-equality-human-right-%E2%80%93-celebrating-women%E2%80%99s-day</ref>. 

Mu ivugurura ry’abaminisitiri ku ya 18 Ukwakira 2018, Espérance Nyirasafari yagizwe Minisitiri w’imikino n’umuco<ref>https://www.minisports.gov.rw/news-detail?tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=9083&cHash=eab184d32afbce78a24ccea469263161</ref>.  Yinjiye muri guverinoma ivuguruye ya Perezida [[Paul Kagame]] wagabanije abagize guverinoma kuva kuri 31 bakagera kuri 26. Inama y'Abaminisitiri ni abagore 50%, ikora u [[Rwanda]], hamwe na [[Etiyopiya]], ibihugu bibiri bya [[Afurika]] byonyine bifite uburinganire muri guverinoma zabo<ref>https://www.migeprof.gov.rw/news-detail/honorable-solina-nyirahabimana-sworn-in-as-new-gender-and-family-promotion-minister</ref>.  

== Umuntu ku giti cye ==
Espérance Nyirasafari numubyeyi wubatse. 
